<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/920059-i-read-this-book-a-few-years-ago-but-since">I read this book a few years ago but since the 2016 presidential election everything I have heard about Donald Trump puts me in mind of Charlie Croker. Was Trump Wolfe&#39;s model for this character? What do other readers think?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_920059'><a id="like_count_community_question_920059" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/920059?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F86172.A_Man_in_Full">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
