<div id="review_19096330" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/19096330" />
    <a title="Gaby" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1018359-gaby"><img alt="Gaby" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1206365631p2/1018359.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/19096330?book_show_action=true">Mar 31, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Gaby" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Gaby" href="/user/show/1018359-gaby">Gaby</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer19096330" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16403497055437699724">I wanted to like this book because it&apos;s set in Atlanta &amp; I like Tom Wolfe. Um, yep, so I wanted to like it. But weighing in at a gajillion pages, if I ever have to read 20 pages about each ancillary character&apos;s italian leather loafers or bowtie type or silk cravat knot&apos;s again, I may shoot myself in the face.</span>
  <span id="freeText16403497055437699724" style="display:none">I wanted to like this book because it's set in Atlanta &amp; I like Tom Wolfe. Um, yep, so I wanted to like it. But weighing in at a gajillion pages, if I ever have to read 20 pages about each ancillary character's italian leather loafers or bowtie type or silk cravat knot's again, I may shoot myself in the face.</span>
