<span id="freeTextContainer17669548589438582986">Wow- What a reading ride !! All well written interesting characters and I will never look at saddlebags without laughing. Only one fly in the ointment was the bank saying it would not foreclose if Crocker vouched for the sterling character of the football star accused of rape. That would have never happened as Crocker owed half a billion.</span>

