        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780553580938" href="/book/show/386419.A_Man_in_Full">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19135352-doubledf99-99?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3801499185" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer366743398996332680">Pretty good read with a rich cast of characters from the workers in the warehouses, prison, the bankers, lawyers, and the rich. Folks living in squalid conditions reading about Stoics, to the rich in their palatial mansions worrying about how to stay afloat and not losing face. And some of the characters rise above it all. The plot thickens as the book moves along like a good batch of chili. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


